{
  "texts": [
    "Many of the things that are dreaded by researchers, such as starting to write, creating coherent structure to text and formulating complex methods, are made a lot easier with the help of GenAI [14,17].",
    "In some ways, it could even be seen as an on-demand reviewer of your manuscript, or a coauthor that assists in writing without the personal disagreements.",
    "Also, when it comes to summarising large bodies of text, GenAI can help grasp and assess information much faster.",
    "A skill that is becoming increasingly important with the ever-growing number of papers that are published each year (although thinking ahead, this would also feed into that problem) [3].",
    "Personally, I strongly believe that when time is saved in the mundane tasks, the freed-up time can be used for critical thinking.This way of thinking about GenAI as an assistant, however, is not shared with everyone."
  ]
}